---

<section class="bg-slate-100 py-20 px-4 sm:px-6">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto text-center">
    <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-primary-color">
      Beneficios que <span class="underline decoration-yellow-400"
        >transforman</span
      > tu negocio
    </h1>
    <p class="text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl mt-2 text-gray-500">
      Descubre cómo nuestros sistemas optimizan tus operaciones y aumentan tu
      productividad
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mt-12">
      <div
        class="card p-8 sm:p-9 bg-white shadow-xl flex flex-col items-center text-center"
      >
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          fill="none"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          stroke-width="1.5"
          stroke="currentColor"
          class="w-12 h-12 text-amber-700 mb-5"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            d="M10.05 4.575a1.575 1.575 0 1 0-3.15 0v3m3.15-3v-1.5a1.575 1.575 0 0 1 3.15 0v1.5m-3.15 0 .075 5.925m3.075.75V4.575m0 0a1.575 1.575 0 0 1 3.15 0V15M6.9 7.575a1.575 1.575 0 1 0-3.15 0v8.175a6.75 6.75 0 0 0 6.75 6.75h2.018a5.25 5.25 0 0 0 3.712-1.538l1.732-1.732a5.25 5.25 0 0 0 1.538-3.712l.003-2.024a.668.668 0 0 1 .198-.471 1.575 1.575 0 1 0-2.228-2.228 3.818 3.818 0 0 0-1.12 2.687M6.9 7.575V12m6.27 4.318A4.49 4.49 0 0 1 16.35 15m.002 0h-.002"
          ></path>
        </svg>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-primary-color">
          Elimina procesos manuales repetitivos
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-500">
          Digitaliza tareas como facturación, inventarios o registros para
          ahorrar horas de trabajo.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div
        class="card p-8 sm:p-9 bg-white shadow-xl flex flex-col items-center text-center"
      >
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          fill="none"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          stroke-width="1.5"
          stroke="currentColor"
          class="w-12 h-12 text-teal-700 mb-5"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            d="m6.115 5.19.319 1.913A6 6 0 0 0 8.11 10.36L9.75 12l-.387.775c-.217.433-.132.956.21 1.298l1.348 1.348c.21.21.329.497.329.795v1.089c0 .426.24.815.622 1.006l.153.076c.433.217.956.132 1.298-.21l.723-.723a8.7 8.7 0 0 0 2.288-4.042 1.087 1.087 0 0 0-.358-1.099l-1.33-1.108c-.251-.21-.582-.299-.905-.245l-1.17.195a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-.98-.314l-.295-.295a1.125 1.125 0 0 1 0-1.591l.13-.132a1.125 1.125 0 0 1 1.3-.21l.603.302a.809.809 0 0 0 1.086-1.086L14.25 7.5l1.256-.837a4.5 4.5 0 0 0 1.528-1.732l.146-.292M6.115 5.19A9 9 0 1 0 17.18 4.64M6.115 5.19A8.965 8.965 0 0 1 12 3c1.929 0 3.716.607 5.18 1.64"
          ></path>
        </svg>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-primary-color">
          Accesibilidad desde cualquier lugar
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-500">
          Accede a tu sistema 24/7 desde computadoras, tablets o móviles con
          internet.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div
        class="card p-8 sm:p-9 bg-white shadow-xl flex flex-col items-center text-center"
      >
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          fill="none"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          stroke-width="1.5"
          stroke="currentColor"
          class="w-12 h-12 text-green-700 mb-5"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            d="M12 6v12m-3-2.818.879.659c1.171.879 3.07.879 4.242 0 1.172-.879 1.172-2.303 0-3.182C13.536 12.219 12.768 12 12 12c-.725 0-1.45-.22-2.003-.659-1.106-.879-1.106-2.303 0-3.182s2.9-.879 4.006 0l.415.33M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z"
          ></path>
        </svg>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-primary-color">
          Ahorro en costos operativos
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-500">
          Reduce gastos en papel, almacenamiento físico o personal
          administrativo.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div
        class="card p-8 sm:p-9 bg-white shadow-xl flex flex-col items-center text-center"
      >
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          fill="none"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          stroke-width="1.5"
          stroke="currentColor"
          class="w-12 h-12 text-indigo-500"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            d="M15.042 21.672 13.684 16.6m0 0-2.51 2.225.569-9.47 5.227 7.917-3.286-.672Zm-7.518-.267A8.25 8.25 0 1 1 20.25 10.5M8.288 14.212A5.25 5.25 0 1 1 17.25 10.5"
          ></path>
        </svg>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-primary-color">
          Trámites ciudadanos en línea
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-500">
          Reduce filas físicas con solicitudes, pagos y seguimiento digital.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div
        class="card p-8 sm:p-9 bg-white shadow-xl flex flex-col items-center text-center"
      >
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          fill="none"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          stroke-width="1.5"
          stroke="currentColor"
          class="w-12 h-12 text-amber-500 mb-5"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            d="m3.75 13.5 10.5-11.25L12 10.5h8.25L9.75 21.75 12 13.5H3.75Z"
          ></path>
        </svg>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-primary-color">
          Agiliza trámites ciudadanos
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-500">
          Portal de autogestión con seguimiento en tiempo real y notificaciones.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
